item.title: CVE-2023-23452|2023-02-20T00:00:00 -- n%2Fa -- fx0-gpnt%20v3%20firmware
item.description: Missing Authentication for Critical Function in SICK FX0-GPNT v3 Firmware Version V3.04 and V3.05 allows an unprivileged remote attacker to achieve arbitrary remote code execution via maliciously crafted RK512 commands to the listener on TCP port 9000.
